node.text:
Welcome to the Berkshires. ⁠⁠⁠
⁠⁠⁠
Situated at the end of a country road, overlooking the Williams River, sits this remarkable Contemporary home on 9 acres. Equipped with countless features and amenities, this home will keep you occupied all year long. The open floor plan provides the perfect layout for everyday living and entertaining. Enjoy all four seasons to their fullest in this gorgeous Massachusetts home. ⁠⁠⁠
⁠⁠⁠
9 Buttondown Lane, Great Barrington, MA⁠⁠⁠
$3,200,000⁠⁠⁠
4 Bedrooms⁠⁠⁠
4/1 Baths⁠⁠⁠
⁠⁠⁠
Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this stunning home, listed with @PatriceMelluzzo of @LivingBerkshires and @WilliamPittSIR.⁠⁠⁠
⁠⁠⁠
#WPSIRListings #WPSIRGreatBarrington #WPSIRTheBerkshiers #BeyondTheCity #SothebysRealty #WPSIR #InTheBerkshiers
